<hr>
<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br><br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Author&#8217;s Name. &#34;Title of Chapter.&#34; <em>Title of Book</em>. Publisher, year of publication, page numbers of chapter.  
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author&#8217;s Name">Knowles, Malcolm S.</span> 
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="Title of Chapter">Independent Study.</span>&#34;
	<span class="hover" title="Title of Book"><em>Using Learning Contracts</em></span>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Jossey-Bass</span>,
	<span class="hover" title="Year of Publication">1986</span>,
	<span class="hover" title="Page numbers">pp. 89-120</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
